The paper proposes a deep learning model for detecting and classifying microscopic foraminifera, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) techniques. The model is based on transfer learning, which is a common approach in computer vision and machine learning research. The paper also introduces a new image dataset, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
